{"tid":1572263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「官方認證」政府強烈譴責示威者暴力行為","createTime":"2019-09-15T15:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T17:07:14.000Z","uid":33307,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c68e7c59f27b62bd4c05153b73632fcb5c1bd729","tid":1572263,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:37:23.000Z","msg":"都係國旗最緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　政府發言人今日（九月十五日）強烈譴責激進示威者在港島區的暴力行為，他們危害市民安全，嚴重破壞社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n　　示威者不理會警方的反對通知書，在銅鑼灣、灣仔和中區一帶進行非法遊行和集會，其中有人更以雜物堵塞多條主要交通幹道，嚴重影響港島區的交通。一些激進示威者向政府總部投擲多枚汽油彈和磚塊，在金鐘和灣仔一帶多處縱火，肆意破壞港鐵站；<span style=\"color: red;\">亦有違法人士在灣仔一間酒店外焚燒國旗，挑戰國家主權。</span><br />\n<br />\n　　政府對這些目無法紀的暴力行為，予以最強烈的譴責。面對激進示威者的暴力衝擊，警方果斷地作出驅散和拘捕，以保障市民安全和恢復社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n　　政府發言人重申，使用暴力手段絕對不是解決問題的方法，只會令整個社會受到傷害。為解決當前的困局，<span style=\"color: green;\">政府已展示了最大的誠意，希望透過溝通平台與市民展開對話</span>，共同解決社會深層次的問題。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年9月15日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間23時11分"},{"pid":"d9eaac712628eeb33b20dd1e44adb77600bec199","tid":1572263,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:38:08.000Z","msg":"毛澤東語錄：<br />\n<br />\n「我認為，對我們來說，一個人，一個黨，一個軍隊，或者一個學校，如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界線，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。」<br />\n〈被敵人反對是好事而不是壞事〉，1939年5月26日<br />\n<br />\n「凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。」<br />\n〈和中央社、掃蕩報、新民報三記者的談話〉，1939年9月16日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/billyhchl/1395111272-2093897685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fbillyhchl%2F1395111272-2093897685.jpg&h=e45e7ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多謝手足，除暴安良，保家衛民，核爆都唔割席。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DNgrNs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DNgrNs.png&h=79213bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抗爭社運mv - Protest Times   Never back down<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bXgpGFTuK54\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbXgpGFTuK54&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=0c6767da\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bXgpGFTuK54</a>"},{"pid":"e50708b53acb12a09fcd8739383d3027911ef722","tid":1572263,"uid":3208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:38:12.000Z","msg":"訓啦柒頭"},{"pid":"d292b922bb6be9bba53d26fc7e220f920b63f3e5","tid":1572263,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:38:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UzI-CgqSL5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUzI-CgqSL5Q&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=8e617071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UzI-CgqSL5Q</a>"},{"pid":"3f6d01a0cf68cfa5eedb2b15f4db55bdab631654","tid":1572263,"uid":259675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"都係支旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950d4fabf675837b613cacd4e6a180ebad1cf56e","tid":1572263,"uid":247032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:38:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老味刀手同火水唔撚講？"},{"pid":"0ceebcd34ff7d118e0d3a7939278cb5c1d7cfd52","tid":1572263,"uid":44980,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:38:59.000Z","msg":"政府使用暴力手段絕對不是解決問題的方法，只會令整個社會受到傷害"},{"pid":"249776f356f2e0c126c9c396f17b91fe290a34ff","tid":1572263,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:39:10.000Z","msg":"收皮啦分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf